Setup
-----

Install isync notmuch msmtp

Insert passwords in ~/.mailpass-<account_name>.gpg
chmod 600 ~/.mailpass-*.gpg

ln -s ~/src/emacs.d/mail/conf/mbsyncrc ~/.mbsyncrc && chmod 600 ~/.mbsyncrc
ln -s ~/src/emacs.d/mail/conf/msmtprc ~/.msmtprc && chmod 600 ~/.msmtprc
ln -s ~/src/emacs.d/mail/conf/notmuch-config ~/.notmuch-config && chmod 600 ~/.notmuch-config
ln -s ~/src/emacs.d/mail/bin/mailfetcher ~/bin/mailfetcher && chmod 700 ~/bin/mailfetcher
ln -s ~/src/emacs.d/mail/lisp/50-email.el ~/src/emacs.d/lisp/enabled/50-email.el


Run
---

mailfetcher

echo -e "This is a test mail" | msmtp -d blabla@gmail.com

Troubelshootings
----------------

Import certs: openssl s_client -starttls imap -connect some.imap.server:port -showcerts

